    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you say that but it doesn't feel true. she works all day and then comes here just to help me with my meds and keep me fed. it feels like i'm just taking up her life. i want things to be easier for her. i want her to be able to live her own life without always worrying about me.",
